# Sample Brain - Project Rule

## Source of truth
- Prefer repository code (`src/`) and tests (`tests/`) over assumptions.
- Keep command examples aligned with `src/cli.py`.

## Safety
- Never write machine-local paths or secrets into tracked files.
- Preserve graceful fallback behavior for optional embedding backends.

## Change style
- Keep edits scoped and minimal.
- Update tests when behavior changes.
- For schema/data contract changes in `src/db.py`, verify affected pipeline modules (`scan`, `analyze`, `classify`, `embed`, `index`, `search`).
